{"tid":2083540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 發威　包辦整週本週音樂節目冠軍！","createTime":"2020-06-28T22:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T05:55:23.000Z","uid":205928,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"21dae131abbddbaae8ad4ca7f31e76be5fe542bc","tid":2083540,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T22:44:58.000Z","msg":"IZ*ONE 今天不僅在出道後首度征服《人氣歌謠》，也迅速地成為六冠王了，恭喜她們啊！<br />\n<br />\n今天（28 日）在 SBS 播出的《人氣歌謠》中，IZ*ONE 以最新主打歌「幻想童話」擊敗了勁敵 TWICE 和最近翻紅的 BLOO，拿下了 6 月第四週的冠軍頭銜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mGFOuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mGFOuK.png&h=f0300f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 自從上週回歸後，無論在實體唱片銷量或音源方面都獲得佳績，本週二也在 SBS MTV《The Show 5》中拿下回歸後首座獎盃，並從此開始連續六天獲獎，在出道後首度寫下「包辦整週冠軍頭銜」的紀錄，獎盃數也已逼近她們目前的最佳成績（七座）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIZ*ONE WORLD DOMINATION"},{"pid":"e0dae7bcc0767cd62ed1a43125938d5387d77038","tid":2083540,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T22:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.koreastardaily.com/tc/amp/127951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Famp%2F127951&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=8608cc62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goo